title: They Were Ten (2009) (Sosich)cbr
description:
October 23,1812:Napoleon troops are abandoning Moscow in hasye,leaving the city to the Cossacks and lootes thirsty for vengeance looking for thefts.They were ten,led by Jean-Baptiste Grassien,doctor in the French army,to flee the Russians,cold,hunger,fatigue and fear...They thought of nothing,except to move forward,one step after another,and another...They were ten in the middle of an ice-cold land,with death and russian cold that began to spread...

enjoy
happy holidays
